Package cinema

Interface MainDisplayPage

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DisplayStaffPage, DisplayUserPage
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomerApp, StaffApp
    interface MainDisplayPage
    Main boundary class between the user and the rest of the application. Responsible for console display of menu options for the user. Calls UserDisplayPage and StaffDisplayPage for menu options for the respective modules.
    Since:
    2019-11-13
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Myat Hmu Khin, Lim Wai Leong
    See Also:
    DisplayUserPage, DisplayStaffPage
